<p><strong>TERMS AND CONDITIONS: <br>Our ''T''s and C''s''<br><br></strong><strong>Baby Kooky Ltd</strong><br>Unit 4D the Green, <br>Green Street, <br>Macclesfield, <br>SK10 1JH<br>01625 400 107<br><br>Our T’s and C’s don’t list all of the provisions set in the (Distance Selling) Regulations 2000, however we are committed to abide by these regulations&nbsp;<br><br><strong>Prices<br></strong><br>The prices payable for goods that you order are as set out in the website. <br>We try to ensure that all the prices shown on this website are accurate. However, occasionally products are mispriced. <br>Where a product''s correct price is lower than the stated price we may issue a refund for the difference and dispatch the order in the usual way. <br>Where a product''s correct price is higher than the stated price we will inform you of the correct price and give you the opportunity to proceed with the order at the correct price or cancel the order.&nbsp;<br>Our delivery charges are set out in our listings.<br>•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>Price and availability information is subject to change without notice.<br>•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>All prices include VAT (where applicable) at the applicable current UK rate.<br>•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>If during processing we discover for any unforeseen reason that we cannot complete order we will cancel the order and email you explaining why (for instance, a stock shortage, inability to obtain payment, or the identification of a pricing, product, or product description fault).<br><br><strong>Cancelling an order:</strong>&nbsp;<br><br>You may cancel your order with us at any time prior to the dispatch of your items.<br>To cancel your order you must notify us by email, or by phone 01625 400 107 (leaving a voice mail is not considered notification of cancellation)<br><br>Please note: Items can be dispatched up to 7 hours prior to a dispatch notification being sent. If you request a cancellation in this 7 hour window and your item has already been dispatched you can refuse to accept the package from the courier and it will be returned directly to us at no extra cost or inconvenience to yourself, this only applies to UK residents.&nbsp;<br><br>If your goods were dispatched before you cancelled the order then you must send the goods back to us at your own cost and risk in the original packaging and condition. Our returns address is:<br><strong>Returns@ <br>Baby Kooky Ltd</strong><br>Unit 4D the green<br>Green Street<br>Macclesfield<br>SK10 1JH<br><br>Please pack the items so that they will not be damaged in transit. Include a copy of the packing note included in the package we sent to you and a brief note of the reason for return.<br><br><br></p><p><br /></p>
</div>

<div id="country5" class="tabcontent">
<strong>Returns<br></strong><br>You may return an item to us at any time prior to 7 days of receiving the item.<br><br>If you receive an item that you did not order, please notify us as soon as possible.<br><br>If your goods were dispatched before you cancel the order then you must send the goods back to us at your own cost and risk in the original packaging and condition. <br><br>Our returns address is:<br><strong><em>Baby Kooky Ltd</em></strong><br>Unit 4D the green<br>Green Street<br>Macclesfield<br>SK10 1JH<br><br>Please pack items so that they will not be damaged in transit. Include a copy of the packing note included in the package we sent to you and a brief note of the reason for return.<br>Once we''ve received the returned or cancelled goods back into our possession, we will endeavor to re-credit your account within 48<br>hours. <br>If you do not pay the costs of return delivery where applicable, we shall be entitled to deduct the direct costs of recovering the goods from the amount to be re-credited to you.<br><br><strong>Cancellation by us</strong><br><br>We reserve the right to cancel the order:<br>•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>If we have insufficient stock to deliver the goods you have ordered<br>•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>If address changes required after your order is completed. (We will not change delivery address’ once an order is received – we will cancel the order so you can re-order with the correct details)<br>•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>If we cannot obtain payment<br>•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>If a product, price, or offer description fault has been identified<br>•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>If we do not deliver to your area<br><br>In the unlikely event we do cancel your contract we will notify you by e-mail and will re-credit your account any moneys deducted immediately.<br><br>We reserve the right to withdraw any products from this website at any time and/or remove or edit any materials or content on this website. We may refuse to process a transaction for any reason or refuse service to anyone at any time at our sole discretion. We will not be liable to you or any third party by reason of our withdrawing any product from this website whether or not that product has been sold; removing or editing any materials or content on the website; refusing to process a transaction or unwinding or suspending any transaction after processing has begun.<br><br><strong>Damaged, Defective or Wrongly sent Items</strong><br><br>Please do not accept or sign for an order which is visibly <em><strong>damaged</strong></em>. If you receive an item which has been damaged in transit, please ask the courier to return it to us. Contact us as soon as possible and will do our best to provide a replacement as quickly as we can.<br><br>In the unlikely event that you receive an item which proves to be <em><strong>faulty</strong></em> we are happy to help. However, we do ask that you notify us of any problem within a reasonable period of time.<br><br>If we have sent the <em><strong>wrong item</strong></em>, firstly we do apologise, unfortunately we are all human and mistakes do happen, please could you email a picture of the item you receive and contact us, we shall endeavor to get the correct item to you asap.<br><div></div>
