<div id="country3" class="tabcontent">
<h3>SHIPPING INFORMATION</h3><br>Items are dispatched daily from our warehouse, if payment is received before 2pm your item will be shipped that day. We aim to dispatch orders within 24 hours Monday to Friday. (Weekend orders will be dispatched on a Monday)<br><br><strong>Royal mail &nbsp;<img src="http://shared1.ad-lister.co.uk/UserImages/4868b927-4d7c-403a-914f-7d9d5d4b826e/Img/_design/royal.jpg"><br></strong><br>We use Royal Mail to ship our none courier items, delivery times are available below.&nbsp;<br>Delivery times are only an estimate. If you require a guarantee, items must be sent by courier. This is advisable at busy times of the year.<br><br><strong>Interlink &amp; UPS &nbsp;<img src="http://shared1.ad-lister.co.uk/UserImages/4868b927-4d7c-403a-914f-7d9d5d4b826e/Img/_design/interlinkups.jpg"><br></strong><br>We use Interlink and UPS as couriers for our items; if a mobile number is supplied upon purchase you will receive a text notification with an hour window of delivery for your item. You will also receive an email notification of delivery<br><br><strong>UK&nbsp;<img src="http://shared1.ad-lister.co.uk/UserImages/4868b927-4d7c-403a-914f-7d9d5d4b826e/Img/_design/map.jpg" style="float: right;"></strong><br><br>Courier delivery is for mainland UK only. For other destinations please contact us before purchasing for an accurate shipping charge.<br><br><strong>Scottish Highlands, Islands, Northern Ireland, Isle of Man and Isles of Scilly</strong> will all incur a surcharge please see the map and contact before purchase to confirm.<br><br>Any items purchased before contact from these areas will have payments refunded and cancellation notices placed to eBay.<br><br><strong>INTERNATIONAL</strong><br><br>We are able to ship anywhere in the world by courier, if you require an item urgently please contact us with the destination postcode and full address for an accurate courier cost. Please note if there is no shipping price showing on the listing page to your country the item will have to be sent by courier due to size and weight. Please contact us before purchase for your shipping cost<br><br><strong>Delivery Estimates<br></strong><br><strong>UK</strong><br><br>Expected delivery times after items are dispatched:<br>Royal Mail 2nd Class - 2-3 business day delivery,&nbsp;<br>Royal mail Tracked 48 - Delivered within 2 business days<br>Courier - Delivered next business day<br><br><strong>INTERNATIONAL</strong><br><br><strong>Standard Airmail delivery times&nbsp;<br></strong>Western Europe 5-10 days<br>Rest of Europe 10-15 days<br>North America 10-14 days&nbsp;<br>Middle East 10-14 days&nbsp;<br>Far East and Australasia 14-21 days&nbsp;<br>Central and S. America 14-21 days<br><br><strong>Airsure &amp; International Signed for</strong> delivery times are generally quicker than standard Airmail<br><br>Delivery aims are in working days (Monday to Friday) and exclude day of posting, Saturdays and Sundays<br><br>Delivery times from Royal Mail are only an estimate. If you require a guarantee, items must be sent by courier. This is advisable at busy times of the year.
