tch notification being sent. If you request a cancellation in this 7 hour window and your item has already been dispatched you can refuse to accept the package from the courier and it will be returned directly to us at no extra cost or inconvenience to yourself, this only applies to UK residents.&nbsp;<br><br>If your goods were dispatched before you cancelled the order then you must send the goods back to us at your own cost and risk in the original packaging and condition. Our returns address is:<br><strong>Returns@ <br>Baby Kooky Ltd</strong><br>Unit 4D the green<br>Green Street<br>Macclesfield<br>SK10 1JH<br><br>Please pack the items so that they will not be damaged in transit. Include a copy of the packing note included in the package we sent to you and a brief note of the reason for return.<br><br><br></p><p><br /></p>
</div>

<div id="country5" class="tabcontent">
<strong>Returns<br></strong><br>You may return an item to us at any time prior to 7 days of receiving the item.<br><br>If you receive an item that you did not order, please notify us as soon as possible.<br><br>If your goods were dispatched before you cancel the order then you must send the goods back to us at your own cost and risk in the original packaging and condition. <br><br>Our returns address is:<br><strong><em>Baby Kooky Ltd</em></strong><br>Unit 4D the green<br>Green Street<br>Macclesfield<br>SK10 1JH<br><br>Please pack items so that they will not be damaged in transit. Include a copy of the packing note included in the package we sent to you and a brief note of the reason for return.<br>Once we''ve received the returned or cancelled goods back into our possession, we will endeavor to re-credit your account within 48<br>hours. <br>If you do not pay the costs of return delivery where applicable, we shall be entitled to deduct the direct costs of recovering the goods from the amount to be re-credited to you.<br><br><strong>Cancellation by us</strong><br><br>We reserve the right to cancel the order:<br>•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>If we have insufficient stock to deliver the goods you have ordered<br>•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>If address changes required after your order is completed. (We will not change delivery address’ once an order is received – we will cancel the order so you can re-order with the correct details)<br>•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>If we cannot obtain payment<br>•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>If a product, price, or offer description fault has been identified<br>•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>If we do not deliver to your area<br><br>In the unlikely event we do cancel your contract we will notify you by e-mail and will re-credit your account any moneys deducted immediately.<br><br>